Notes:
Generally, raspi boards use cmdline.txt, config.txt
while non-uefi boards (nxp and rockchip) boards use
joetooEnv.txt, boot.cmd, boot.scr ...

However, librecomputer amlogic boards support uefi,
so, starting with solitude, I'm deploying the boot-firmware
** w/o ** boot config files (use boot files from armbian
image instead)
